bbsdoors a better BBS Door echo
by: Rob Mooney
    1:323/1017

BBSDOORS echo was formed by me Rob Mooney just recently due to the
unjust and inappropriate heavy handed censorship that I've found in
another of the fidonet echo's that deals with BBS Doors.

This echo completely deal's with BBS Doors, their technical support,
Distribution and online Registration site's, new releases & update's
for all doors for all BBS platforms. I am hoping to have ALL Door
Authors new and old join this echo and offer their support to
everyone who is here.

If you've ever wanted to know about a BBS Door before you've spent
the time and money to download or freq it, or you are sick of reading
nonsense messages from people who have no aim in life other than to
flame a Door Author or complain about a Door because they have had
a hard time with it and elected not to take the time to seek proper
support then this is the place for you.

I can guarantee that everyone who joins this echo will be treated the
same. NO favoritism will be shown to ANYONE at all. Comply with the
very basic set of rules and you'll be OK!

For more information of how to receive this echo or to help me with my
endeavor to get BBSDOORS on the backbone please contact Rob Mooney at
1:323/1017.

